{"tid":1656491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院加速審議香港人權與民主法案","createTime":"2019-10-15T15:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T15:18:00.000Z","uid":265112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"787f289f78861defe9caef8126dbcc72bc5018c3","tid":1656491,"uid":265112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"今天（10月15日）下午三點半(美國時間），美國國會眾議院要投票是否加速通過8個法案。其中三個是關於香港的，包括香港人權與民主法案，保護香港法案。如果加速通過的動議被通過。這些法案將在今晚6:30被投票。中間沒有辯論過程。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtAIPjABiQD3qjlEl1T5VpA/community?lb=UgztDKBpHnqoKVBb2ZZ4AaABCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtAIPjABiQD3qjlEl1T5VpA%2Fcommunity%3Flb%3DUgztDKBpHnqoKVBb2ZZ4AaABCQ&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=91995c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtAIPjABiQD3qjlEl1T5VpA/community?lb=UgztDKBpHnqoKVBb2ZZ4AaABCQ</a>"},{"pid":"23c1fc42a5d476a29680a5dd190a1f490ca39464","tid":1656491,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}